    {
      "id": "i7-q10",
      "type": "code",
      "question": "Kisa bir Security konfigurasyonu yaz: `/public/**` acik, diger endpointler authenticated olsun ve uygulama OAuth2 Resource Server olarak JWT kabul etsin.",
      "starterCode": "class SecurityConfig {\n    // TODO\n}",
      "answerCode": "@Configuration\n@EnableWebSecurity\nclass SecurityConfig {\n\n    @Bean\n    SecurityFilterChain filterChain(HttpSecurity http) throws Exception {\n        return http\n            .csrf(csrf -> csrf.disable())\n            .authorizeHttpRequests(auth -> auth\n                .requestMatchers(\"/public/**\").permitAll()\n                .anyRequest().authenticated()\n            )\n            .oauth2ResourceServer(oauth2 -> oauth2.jwt(Customizer.withDefaults()))\n            .build();\n    }\n}",
      "answerBody": "### Dogru Cevap\nAsagidaki referans kodu inceleyebilirsin.",
